Package sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.model.entities

package sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.model.entities
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Application
    Represents an application made by an HDB applicant for a BTO project.
    Block
    Represents a residential block within a BTO project.
    BTOExercise
    Represents a BTO Exercise that groups multiple BTO Projects together.
    BTOProj
    Represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) project managed by HDB.
    Enquiry
    Represents an enquiry made by an applicant regarding a BTO project.
    Flat
    Represents a flat (unit) within a residential block.
    FlatType
    Represents a type of flat in a BTO project.
    HDBApplicant
    Represents an HDB Applicant user.
    HDBManager
    Represents an HDB Manager who manages BTO projects and officer applications.
    HDBOfficer
    Represents an HDB Officer who handles assigned BTO projects and officer applications.
    OfficerProjectApplication
    Represents an officer's application to be assigned to a BTO project.
    ProjectMessage
    Represents a single message exchanged in a project enquiry thread.
    User
    Represents an abstract base class for all users in the system.
